==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Queue
<hw>Queue</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Cue</er>.]</ety> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A tail-like appendage of hair; a
pigtail.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A line of persons waiting
anywhere.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Queue</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Queue
<hw>Queue</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To fasten, as hair, in a
queue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quey</ent>⟦br⟧
